cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a deep neural network model for fine-grained recognition using meta-learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The model also involves pairwise comparison and alignment of image features, which relates to the areas of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL) that deal with similarity and distance metrics. Finally, the paper evaluates the model on several datasets, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
